            "block_wrapper_classes": "col-span-12 flex justify-center  px-4 items-center text-center relative",
            "block_title": "",
            "title_classes": "text",
            "description": "<h2 class=\"text-center font-bebas text-2xl lg:text-4xl\">☀️Made for Summer Adventures☀️</h2>\n<br>\n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\nWhether you’re heading to the beach, jetting off on holiday, or just soaking up sun in the garden, we’ve got everything you need for the ultimate summer. \n</p> <br> \n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\nFirst up, underwear. Stock up on our summer underwear bestsellers – from breathable <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/bamboo-boxer-shorts\" class=\"link\">Men’s Bamboo Boxers</a> and <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/womens-bamboo\" class=\"link\">Women’s Bamboo Boxers</a> (perfect for sweaty days) to our classic <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/mens-loose-fit-boxers\" class=\"link\">Men’s Loose Fit Boxers</a>, <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/his-briefs\" class=\"link\">Briefs</a>, and Women’s <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/ladies-thongs\" class=\"link\">Thongs</a>, <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/her-individuals\" class=\"link\">Briefs</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/seamless-underwear\" class=\"link\">Seamless</a> styles. And don’t miss our brand-new summer prints like <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/hibiscus\" class=\"link\">Hibiscus</a>, <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/hawaii\" class=\"link\">Hawaii</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/oddballs-subscriptions\" class=\"link\">Calypso</a>.\n\n</p> <br> \n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\nPlanning your summer holiday? Grab one of our NEW <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/quick-dry-towels\" class=\"link\">Quick Dry Towels</a> – lightweight, microfibre and fast-drying, they’re a game-changer for beach trips, poolside lounging, or even festivals. If you prefer a classic style, we’ve still got cotton <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/cotton-towel\" class=\"link\">Beach Towels</a> left too – but be quick!\n\n</p> <br> \n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\nOur summer accessories are designed to go wherever you do. <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/socks/style-trainer\" class=\"link\">Trainer Socks</a> keep things cool and comfy under trainers or sliders. <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/sunglasses\" class=\"link\">Sunglasses</a>,  <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/beach-bag\" class=\"link\">Beach Bags</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/wash-bags\" class=\"link\">Travel Wash Bags</a> are the ultimate add-ons – and you can even get them as a <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/free-gift\" class=\"link\">free product</a> when you spend over £40! Throw in a <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/water-bottle\" class=\"link\">water bottle</a> and one of our <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/fleece-blanket\" class=\"link\">cosy blankets</a> for those colder evenings and you’re set. \n\n</p> <br> \n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\n\nWant to keep things simple? Use our Summer Bundle Builder to mix and match your favourite <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/pages/shop-by-design#popular\" class=\"link\">summer underwear</a> in one easy, holiday-ready haul. Choose from <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/swimming-shorts\" class=\"link\">classic mesh-lined swim shorts</a>, <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/mens-swim-shorts-with-compression-liner\" class=\"link\">compression-lined swim shorts</a> for extra support, or go streamlined with our <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/swimmers\" class=\"link\">men’s swim briefs</a>. Pair them with underwear and accessories to build your ultimate summer bundle in just a few clicks.\n\n</p> <br> \n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\nHowever you're spending summer 2025 — whether it's a weekend escape, a family holiday, a sunny getaway, or a wild one with friends - do it the bold way. Make it a summer to remember with OddBalls! \n\n</p>",
            "description_classes": "",
            "svg": ""
          }
        }
      },
